title: product1
description: He is a gentleman, straight as an arrow; responsible and dependable but he has a weakness for speed. He gets high on the feeling of the pistons pumping underneath the car as the wind whips through his hair and the smooth engine powers along the highway at a fast clip. He is passionate about his car and the sleek dynamics of the machine speak to him. For the man who appreciates and adores the speed and curves on a classic automobile, Jaguar presents a luxury Eau de Toilette that spreads the aura of power and confidence. It is a classic fragrance that has been established and accepted as masterpiece, almost an icon in the fragrance wall of fame.
